<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870708-0110 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News:Lewis Galoob Toys Inc.</HL><DD> 07/08/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> WNEWS GATO </IN><DATELINE> LEWIS GALOOB TOYS INC. (San Francisco)  </DATELINE><TEXT>    Mark D. Goldman,37 years old, was named executive vice president and chiefoperating officer of this toy maker. He succeeds RobertGaloob, 33, who left the concern to pursue non-toy relatedventures, the company said. Mr. Goldman previously wasexecutive vice president and chief operating officer of AgesEntertainment Software Inc., a Gulf andamp; Western Inc. developerand marketer of video games.</TEXT></DOC>